title: Add more nn docs
body_html:
Addresses #1578. Two main changes:

  • For functions that had documentation elsewhere, added minor docs and links to the docs elsewhere
  • For functions that didn't have docs elsewhere and were missing args/return type docs, document the args and return types

Test Plan

make html to build sphinx, view in browser and check that documentation now exists.

body:
Addresses #1578. Two main changes:

- For functions that had documentation elsewhere, added minor docs and links to the docs elsewhere
- For functions that didn't have docs elsewhere and were missing args/return type docs, document the args and return types

### Test Plan
`make html` to build sphinx, view in browser and check that documentation now exists.
